race.comment: WEST ON COLE (1) missed the frame last time when fifth (30.28) at Cannington but prior to that had two placings in a row. Form here sound including four wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and can bounce back. STU MCFLY (2) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 7 lengths (27.38) at this track. Capable of going close again. ASTON WALKER (4) jumped from box 2 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.37. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to feature again. CABIN CREW (5) missed the frame latest (28.33) when fourth over 488m at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.
